# Incentive Calculator — Product Domain

Implement features and mocks against this module map. Preserve role semantics (Sales → self, Manager → team, Admin → org).

## 1. Dashboard (Executive Overview)
- KPIs: total incentive earned; target vs achieved; achievement %; pending vs paid
- Visuals: monthly/quarterly trends; revenue vs incentive
- Insights: over/under performance flags; optional AI suggestions
- Activity: recent deals; incentive updates

## 2. Incentive Calculator Engine (Core Logic)
- Inputs: revenue/sales value; deals closed; configurable KPI inputs
- Rules: slab/tier incentives; role/seasonal multipliers; accelerators (overachievement)
- Engine: real-time payout; retroactive adjustments; what-if simulation; historical plan versions

## 3. Performance Tracking
- Individual: sales vs targets; conversion; deal velocity
- Team: team vs individual; weekly/monthly/quarterly time intelligence
- Drill-down: user → deal → KPI; alerts on drops and goals nearing

## 4. Leaderboard & Gamification
- Rankings: revenue, incentive, KPI score; filters (period, region/team)
- Gamification: badges; rank movement (↑↓); optional rewards/points

## 5. Incentive Breakdown Engine
- Split: base, variable, bonus/accelerator; drill-down by deal, KPI, time
- Audit: calculation logs; rules applied; export Excel/PDF

## 6. Scenario Simulation (Advanced)
- Scenario builder (e.g. “close N more deals”); current vs projected; sensitivity on KPIs; side-by-side views; forecast charts

## 7. Reporting & Analytics
- Reports: summary, detailed breakdown, leaderboard; scheduling; Excel/PDF/CSV; historical trends; compliance-oriented outputs

## 8. Targets & Goals Management
- Setup: revenue and KPI targets; individual vs team allocation; completion %; nearing/missed alerts; optional dynamic adjustment

## 9. Admin & Configuration
- Plan builder: slabs, tiers, multipliers; KPI weights; user roles; plan assignment by role/team; approval workflows before payout

## 10. Data Integration Layer
- CRM: Salesforce, HubSpot; Excel/CSV import; API sync; batch jobs; validation, errors, deduplication

## 11. User Profile & Settings
- Profile, assigned targets, plans; RBAC; notifications (email, in-app)
